#!F-adobe-helvetica-medium-r-normal--18*
#!N 
#!CSeaGreen #!N  #!Rresize Moving and Resizing Windows #!N #!EC #!N 
#!N You can move windows and adjust their sizes on the 
screen. #!N #!N To move a window, drag the window name 
portion of the title bar to the desired screen location. #!N 
#!N To resize a window, do one of the following: #!N 
#!I0 #!N  #!F-adobe-times-medium-r-normal--18*   #!N #!N #!I30 #!N o Drag on one 
of the horizontal borders. The window will shrink or expand vertically 
as you drag the border. #!N #!I30 #!N o Drag on 
one of the vertical borders. The window will shrink or expand 
horizontally as you drag the border. #!N #!I30 #!N o Drag 
on one of the corner borders. The window will shrink or 
expand both vertically and horizontally (but not necessarily in a uniform 
fashion) as you drag the border. #!N #!I0 #!N #!EF #!N 
